===============================================================================

PunditPanel installed!

Next steps:

1. Run the migration:
   bin/rails db:migrate

2. Configure the panel in config/initializers/pundit_panel.rb
   - Set user_model to your auth model (e.g., "Admin")
   - Set auth_method to your authentication before_action
   - Set role_attribute to the enum column (for :enum adapter)

3. Visit /pundit_panel to manage permissions

4. (Optional) To use DB-backed permissions in your policies,
   update app/policies/application_policy.rb to inherit from
   PunditPanel::ApplicationPolicy instead of a plain class.

===============================================================================
